- 1× NVIDIA RTX PRO 6000 Blackwell, 96 GB VRAM
- 64 CPU cores, 128 GB RAM
- CUDA 13.0, JAX 0.10.0 + jax-cuda12-plugin
- Use batch sizes of 4096–16384 to fully utilise GPU throughput








